title: Flu cases at record high for time of year as NHS warns of 'unprecedented' outbreak
subtitle: An average of 1,700 patients were in hospital in England with flu last week - more than 50% higher than the same period last year, figures show.
full_text: An average of 1,700 patients were in hospital in England with flu last week - more than 50% higher than the same period last year, figures show.
